行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"dfbf216f0bf37e02c172815968163d3c930396f3","tid":1777413,"uid":269498,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"d8479ebdc17564865364f65472acc4645f8f1f70","tid":1777413,"uid":116054,"like":429,"dislike":0,"score":429,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:13:57.000Z","msg":"我要知陳彥琳媽咪係咪被殺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:49:27.000Z","msg":"HKDI仍然封口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府同警方話涉事資料無需公佈"},{"pid":"79457d37012f6ca678be4edc93a78c12dc88883e","tid":1777413,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:52:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6a10cf1b59578b5f3ea4176171324b75156d1689","tid":1777413,"uid":72058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"295bdeff75f057cba18cd7c6e7d7541d13313278","tid":1777413,"uid":237209,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"dac0e26f96174020352be80ee841a3ff17c31657","tid":1777413,"uid":158270,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"quote":{"pid":"a40a12f5ee212deacfafb4979334b5a21c11a99d","tid":1777413,"uid":24615,"like":134,"dislike":1,"score":133,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:26:31.000Z","msg":"本身聖誕就是朋友約出黎既節日 不過睇黎都係冇ga la<br />\n<br />\n不過新年由廢老主導 即使唔出黎食飯都一定會打電話問好<br />\n<br />\n不得不承認上一代個關係係close好多 親戚失蹤左好難隱瞞"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T09:50:59.000Z","msg":"不得不承認原本以為拜年好麻煩，點知係有個咁嘅用途"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:54:21.000Z","msg":"居然係用嚟睇有冇親戚死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"834510931085ac474e61058629df7571f5c47a93","tid":1777413,"uid":131125,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"dac0e26f96174020352be80ee841a3ff17c31657","tid":1777413,"uid":158270,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"quote":{"pid":"a40a12f5ee21